# Posting Queue Schema

This document defines the required columns in the Google Sheets “Posting Queue” tab.

---

## Required Columns

| Column | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| row_number | number | Unique row identifier used for updates |
| Status | string | Workflow state: Pending / Posted / Errored |
| Media URL | string | Google Drive share link to image/video |
| Title | string | Optional title for internal reference |
| Caption | string | Post caption text |
| Platforms | string | Optional list (comma-separated) |
| Posted At | string | ISO timestamp written when posted |
| Error Message | string | Optional error capture |
| Approved By | string | Optional reviewer name |

---

## Status Values

- **Pending** (recommended for items awaiting post)
- **Posted** (set by workflow on success)
- **Errored** (set by workflow on failure)
